{"id":179,"idInBook":1639,"chapterId":25,"bookId":1,"arabic":"حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ، حَدَّثَنَا الأَعْمَشُ، عَنْ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، عَنِ الأَسْوَدِ، عَنْ عَائِشَةَ ـ رضى الله عنها ـ قَالَتْ أَهْدَى النَّبِيُّ صلى الله عليه وسلم مَرَّةً غَنَمًا‏.‏","english":{"narrator":"Narrated `Aisha:","text":"Once the Prophet (ﷺ) sent sheep as Hadi."},"hadithNumber":1639,"vol":3,"hadithId":179,"reference":"25:179","meta":{"id":"bukhari","length":7563,"totalChapters":97,"arabic":{"title":"صحيح البخاري","author":"الإمام محمد بن إسماعيل البخاري"},"english":{"title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","author":"Imam Muhammad ibn Ismail al-Bukhari"}},"chapter":{"id":25,"bookId":1,"arabic":"كتاب الحج","english":"Hajj (Pilgrimage)","startHadith":1461,"endHadith":1707,"totalHadiths":247},"version":{"name":"bukhari","title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","chapters":97}}